---
// Legacy unprefixed URL — content lives in
// src/content/pages/<kind>/tf-idf/{en,ko}.mdx, served at
// /en/ml/tf-idf/ and /ko/ml/tf-idf/. We keep this file as a
// redirect stub (rather than 404) for any external bookmark or internal link
// that still points at the unprefixed URL. Astro emits static redirect HTML
// with meta refresh + canonical + robots:noindex.
return Astro.redirect("/en/ml/tf-idf/", 301);
